It is operated by the concessionary Aeroporto de Feira de Santana.\n\n==History==\nThe airport was inaugurated in 1985 and since May 29, 2012 operated by the concessionary Aeroporto Feira de Santana formed by [http://www.utc.com.br/estrutura.php?id=204 UTC Engineering] and [http://www.sinart.com.br/ Sinart].\n\n==Airlines and destinations==\n{{Airport-dest-list\n|[[Azul Brazilian Airlines]] | [[Tancredo Neves International Airport|Belo Horizonte\u2013Confins]]\n}}\n\n==Access==\nThe airport is located {{convert|12|km|0|abbr=on}} from downtown Feira de Santana.\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Aviation|Brazil}}\n*[[List of airports in Brazil]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{WAD|SNJD|source=[[DAFIF]]}}\n*{{GCM|SNJD|source=[[DAFIF]]}}\n<!--*{{NWS-current|SNJD}}-->\n*{{ASN|FEC}}\n\n{{Airports in Bahia}}\n{{List of airports}}\n{{Brazil topics}}\n\n[[Category:Airports in Bahia]]\n[[Category:Airports established in 1985]]\n[[Category:Feira de Santana]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox airport\n| name         = Gov. Jo\u00e3o Durval Carneiro Airport\n| nativename   = ''Aeroporto Gov. Jo\u00e3o Durval Carneiro''\n| nativename-a = \n| nativename-r =\n| image        = Aeroporto de Feira de Santana.JPG \n| image-width  = \n| caption      =\n| IATA         = FEC\n| ICAO         = SBFE\n| LID          =\n| GPS          =\n| WMO          =\n| type         = Public\n| owner-oper   =\n| owner        =\n| operator     = Aeroporto Feira de Santana \n| city-served  = [[Feira de Santana]]\n| location     = \n| hub          =\n| metric-elev  = yes\n| elevation-f  = 768\n| elevation-m  = 234\n| website      = \n| coordinates  = {{coord|12|12|11|S|038|54|24|W|region:BR|display=inline,title}}\n| pushpin_map            = Brazil\n| pushpin_label_position = \n| pushpin_label          = FEC\n| pushpin_map_alt        =\n| pushpin_mapsize        = \n| pushpin_image          =\n| pushpin_map_caption    = Location in Brazil\n| metric-rwy   = yes\n| r1-number    = 13/31\n| r1-length-f  